WEBVTT

00:01:01.560 --> 00:01:02.620
You've got skills.

00:01:02.840 --> 00:01:04.480
Seems you've been busy these years.

00:01:04.480 --> 00:01:06.010
To deal with a beast like you

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:07.570
is more than enough.

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:11.120
That habit of yours - being defiant even when facing death

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:12.640
hasn't changed a bit.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.079
Chunyu!

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:32.210
Don't be afraid.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.079
I'm here.

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:43.400
Chunyu!

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:06.160
Chunyu!

00:03:06.160 --> 00:03:07.320
Mom!

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:09.400
Don't go!

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.040
Don't go!

00:03:12.160 --> 00:03:12.960
Chunyu!

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:14.320
Mom!

00:03:16.040 --> 00:03:16.840
Mom!

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.140
It's all right.

00:03:27.240 --> 00:03:28.370
Everything's fine.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.800
It's over now.

00:03:34.880 --> 00:03:35.680
Sister,

00:03:36.079 --> 00:03:37.320
Jiang Chunyu is dead.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.160
What?

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:40.120
Really dead?

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:42.640
I drowned her with my own hands.

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:45.360
Xiaomeng.

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:46.360
Well done.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.200
Let's go

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:48.520
and celebrate.

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.160
Come on.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.800
I thought Jiang Chunyu was quite formidable,

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:10.800
but she's still no match for Gu Nian.

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:12.600
My life from now on

00:04:12.600 --> 00:04:14.260
will probably be even harder.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.240
Nian,

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:20.300
let me toast to you.

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:29.960
Xiaomeng,

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:31.720
have a drink with me.

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:35.680
Nian.

00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:38.330
I'll drink with you.

00:04:58.080 --> 00:04:59.320
Is it good?

00:05:02.440 --> 00:05:03.240
It's good.

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:04.640
Such expensive wine,

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:06.810
how could it not taste good?

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:08.000
Fang Yue,

00:05:08.440 --> 00:05:09.880
do you know why

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:12.640
I've kept you by my side all this time?

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.880
Because you're

00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:18.720
pathetic.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.480
Mr. Mu.

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:51.640
Here's all the information about Jiang Chunyu.

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:53.840
It mostly matches what's on her resume.

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:55.760
However, there's one thing they concealed.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:05:57.159
During her high school years,

00:05:57.159 --> 00:05:58.640
she received a scholarship

00:05:58.640 --> 00:06:01.200
from Shangcheng International High School for her excellent grades.

00:06:01.200 --> 00:06:02.480
But for some unknown reason,

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:04.210
she dropped out shortly after.

00:06:08.840 --> 00:06:09.800
So it's her.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:12.090
No wonder she looked familiar.

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:19.000
Chunyu

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:43.000
I'm still alive.

00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:44.530
How are you feeling?

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:47.460
Are you uncomfortable anywhere?

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.040
Mr. Mu

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.040
Qiushan

00:06:58.480 --> 00:06:59.810
Thank you for saving me.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.360
Actually,

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:08.980
you saved me and Weiwei ten years ago.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.320
Back then, our family

00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:13.000
had a serious car accident.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:15.660
The driver fled the scene.

00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:18.320
My brother and his wife died instantly.

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:20.560
I was almost hit by the car.

00:07:20.640 --> 00:07:22.240
I fell into a coma afterward.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:25.540
Then I suddenly heard a child crying.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:26.820
At that moment,

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:31.240
you appeared.

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:05.960
Vivi.

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:19.060
Vivi, don't be afraid.

00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:20.240
Uncle is here.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.690
So that child from back then

00:08:32.520 --> 00:08:33.320
was Vivi.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:36.600
No wonder

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.330
your attitude toward me

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.179
has been strange from the beginning.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:42.880
Chunyu.

00:08:43.799 --> 00:08:45.080
Can you tell me

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:47.560
who that person was last night?

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:49.020
Why did he want to kill you?

00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:11.200
The enemy who pushed me into a cold hell.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.130
I should have known they would make desperate moves.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:15.440
I was careless.

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:17.760
It won't happen again.

00:09:17.760 --> 00:09:18.690
So in the future,

00:09:19.880 --> 00:09:21.940
you still want to keep fighting them?

00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:25.760
The Gu family has deep roots.

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:28.010
Old Mr. Gu seems easy to get along with,

00:09:28.040 --> 00:09:29.320
but he's actually ruthless

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:31.280
and extremely protective of his family.

00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:32.040
With just you alone,

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:33.800
you can't possibly handle this.

00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:34.600
Ten years.

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.130
I've been preparing for ten years.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:41.160
No matter what happens,

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:43.040
I will never give up.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:45.000
So what if you've prepared for ten years?

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:47.000
You still ended up thrown into the water.

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:48.040
If I had arrived a few minutes later,

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:49.570
you might not even be alive.

00:09:58.560 --> 00:09:59.960
You're worried about me.

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:02.280
Yes.

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:19.440
I want to set a fire,

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:21.840
let the flames spread,

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.520
burn them all to death.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:39.840
Who is it?

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:41.600
So noisy.

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:49.520
Wake up.

00:10:50.520 --> 00:10:51.520
See who's there.

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:54.560
Who is it?

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.640
Hello, delivery.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:58.280
Your pizza is here.

00:11:06.280 --> 00:11:07.080
Sis.

00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:09.210
Drink some honey water.

00:11:09.280 --> 00:11:10.810
It helps with the hangover.

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:19.280
Nian.

00:11:19.280 --> 00:11:20.280
The pizza's here.

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:21.620
Eat while it's hot.

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:25.360
After drinking all night,

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:27.360
I am quite hungry.

00:11:28.400 --> 00:11:29.460
I'll get it for you.

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:06.720
The toy

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:08.560
Who sent it?

00:12:10.520 --> 00:12:11.780
You scared me to death!

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.890
Who's playing pranks so early in the morning?

00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:18.720
That delivery person just now.

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:21.050
What did they look like?

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:24.050
I couldn't see clearly.

00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:31.840
Nian.

00:12:32.280 --> 00:12:34.240
You don't suspect me, do you?

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:46.120
Hey.

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:47.240
Gu Nian.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:49.640
Are you surprised?

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:51.720
Do you like this gift?

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.120
Jiang Chunyu.

00:12:55.400 --> 00:12:57.130
Isn't Jiang Chunyu already...

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:06.360
Did you think I was already dead?

00:13:07.080 --> 00:13:08.440
Sorry to disappoint you.

00:13:08.440 --> 00:13:09.600
I'm too tough to die.

00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:11.970
Just can't seem to kick the bucket.

00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:12.960
We are destined

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:14.880
to be entangled forever.

00:13:16.400 --> 00:13:17.440
Jiang Chunyu.

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:19.720
You think these

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:21.480
childish pranks

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:24.360
will scare me?

00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:26.560
Dream on.

00:13:26.840 --> 00:13:28.570
I forgot to tell you something.

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:31.240
I installed hidden cameras in my rental apartment.

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.360
Last night, Gu Xiaomeng's

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:33.800
entire process of kidnapping

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:36.240
and holding me hostage was recorded clearly.

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.320
If I give this video

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:38.840
to the police and media...

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:40.520
Your dear brother

00:13:41.040 --> 00:13:42.240
is going to prison.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:48.880
What do you want?

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:50.640
What do I want?

00:13:51.160 --> 00:13:52.960
That depends on your sincerity.

00:13:54.760 --> 00:13:56.640
Who do you think you are

00:13:57.200 --> 00:13:58.960
to threaten me?

00:13:59.520 --> 00:14:01.650
Well, since Miss Gu isn't interested,

00:14:01.760 --> 00:14:03.960
I'll have to give this to someone who is.

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:11.600
Oh no.

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:18.800
Chunyu,

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:21.240
why are you in such a hurry

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:22.440
to find Grandpa Gu? What's the matter?

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:23.240
Grandpa Gu,

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:24.880
I

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:30.160
would like you to take a look at this.

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:43.360
Guards!

00:14:44.760 --> 00:14:46.360
Arrest that little brat Gu Xiaomeng

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:47.240
right now!

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:52.240
Tell us

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:53.840
why you kidnapped Jiang Chunyu.

00:14:53.840 --> 00:14:55.240
What the hell do you want?

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:56.520
You dare to be stubborn with me?

00:14:56.520 --> 00:14:58.250
You think I can't deal with you?

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:05.120
Go to hell!

00:15:05.160 --> 00:15:05.960
Bitch!

00:15:06.400 --> 00:15:08.160
You bit me!

00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:17.560
Get them!

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:18.880
Beat them hard!

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:19.560
Yes.

00:15:19.640 --> 00:15:21.440
Beat him until he begs for mercy.

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:24.000
Grandpa!

00:15:24.040 --> 00:15:25.640
Please spare Xiaomeng!

00:15:25.760 --> 00:15:27.200
Xiaomeng was just acting on impulse.

00:15:27.200 --> 00:15:29.240
He definitely won't dare to do it again.

00:15:29.240 --> 00:15:30.360
If you keep beating him,

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.760
someone could die, Grandfather.

00:15:31.760 --> 00:15:33.120
How dare you plead for him?

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:34.960
If Chunyu hadn't been so forgiving,

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:36.840
our Gu family would have lost all face.

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:38.320
I didn't want to raise him in the first place.

00:15:38.320 --> 00:15:39.120
It was you

00:15:39.200 --> 00:15:40.760
who insisted on adopting this little brat.